    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_32_508-543",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "508-543",
      "markText": "他时时准备着解释自己的行为，哪怕是最没有疑问的，另外，他还总是很守时。",
      "totalCount": 1394,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=508&rangeEnd=543",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=508&rangeEnd=543"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_33_1507-1544",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1507-1544",
      "markText": "居住在熟识已久的地方，他感到了安全，正如年迈的老囚重返他所熟识的监牢一般。",
      "totalCount": 588,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1507&rangeEnd=1544",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1507&rangeEnd=1544"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_32_2274-2311",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "2274-2311",
      "markText": "他既强烈渴望出双入对的夫妻生活，又不想失去单身男子有的那种防范性的幽默感。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2274&rangeEnd=2311",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2274&rangeEnd=2311"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_29_575-652",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "575-652",
      "markText": "我只知道构成联系的那个人不见了，腐败的种子进入了他的灵魂。 ——约瑟夫·康拉德",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=652",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=652"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_32_1406-1429",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "1406-1429",
      "markText": "他总是准点返回。这是上了年纪后具有的一种美德。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1406&rangeEnd=1429",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1406&rangeEnd=1429"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_30_717-733",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "717-733",
      "markText": "“我们所想象的故事是出自现实。”",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=717&rangeEnd=733",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=717&rangeEnd=733"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_48_5320-5376",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "5320-5376",
      "markText": "为什么我们有的人就无法去爱成功、权力或是美艳呢？他很纳闷。因为我们觉得自己配不上，还是因为我们更乐意与失败为伍？",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23659616&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5320&rangeEnd=5376",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4d8324d0716904604d83e51?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=5320&rangeEnd=5376"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23659616_34_8286-8307",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "8286-8307",
